---
---
<section class="section" id="services">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
      <h2>Exterior painting is what we do best.</h2>
      <p>We're built around one job done right: protecting and refreshing the outside of your home. Interior and cabinet work are available too, for clients who want one crew for the whole house.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-grid">
      <div class="svc-card svc-featured fade-up">
        <svg class="svc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
          <path d="M3 9l9-6 9 6"/><path d="M5 9v11h14V9"/><path d="M10 20v-6h4v6"/>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <h3>Exterior Painting <span class="badge">Our specialty</span></h3>
          <p>Siding, trim, doors, fascia, and decks — fully prepped, primed, and finished with paint rated for South Sound weather.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#estimate" class="btn btn-light">Get a Free Estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="svc-secondary-head">Also available</p>
    <div class="svc-grid">
      <div class="svc-card fade-up">
        <svg class="svc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
          <path d="M3 21l4-1 11-11-3-3L4 17l-1 4z"/><path d="M14 6l3 3"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Interior Painting</h3>
        <p>Walls, trim, ceilings, and cabinetry, prepped and finished room by room.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card fade-up">
        <svg class="svc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
          <rect x="4" y="3" width="16" height="18" rx="1"/><path d="M4 11h16"/>
          <circle cx="8" cy="7" r="0.6" fill="currentColor"/>
          <circle cx="8" cy="16" r="0.6" fill="currentColor"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Cabinet Refinishing</h3>
        <p>Spray-finished cabinets that look replaced, not repainted.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card fade-up">
        <svg class="svc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
          <path d="M3 21h18"/><path d="M5 21V7l7-4 7 4v14"/>
          <path d="M9 21v-6h6v6"/>
          <path d="M9 11h.01M14 11h.01M9 15h.01M14 15h.01"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Commercial Painting</h3>
        <p>Off-hours scheduling for offices, retail, and multi-unit properties.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
